text: Nizhny Sarabil () is a rural locality (a village) in Tazlarovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 96 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Isyangulovo, 8 km from Tazlarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Nizhny Sarabil
